node.text: This just in! Beginning August 9, the Disney Dream will kick off our long-awaited return to cruising with three- and four-night cruises from Port Canaveral, Florida. node.text: As the sun rose over Magic Kingdom Park this morning, a golden 50th crest glimmered on Cinderella Castle for the first time. @WaltDisneyImagineering installed the final piece of shimmering décor overnight, completing her royal makeover as we ramp up to Walt Disney World’s 50th Anniversary celebration, beginning October 1st. Keep your eye out for more EARidescent décor on the horizon. ✨ #DisneyWorld50

node.text: Just in time for the Oct. 1 start of “The World’s Most Magical Celebration” at @WaltDisneyWorld Resort, visitors to Orlando International Airport will be able to discover exciting Disney touches and new EARidescent magic as part of a wide-spanning art installation including images of favorite Disney characters on the terminal train stations, immersive photo ops with pop-up ride vehicles and a glistening glow of pixie dust to start making special memories as they pass through the airport.
